My GP gave me an article about some strange research entitled "Money Causes Brain Activity, Especially When Others Have Less of It".
So the feelings of the workers on payday are affected by how much everyone else gets.
The experiment was conducted at the University of Bonn using magnetic resonance tomography, and the results were published in the latest issue of Science.
